ledges need to better share kickoff call context](https://fathom.video/share/uzLphizGENVWAcHcGLNW9mzb_HYPrCKo?tab=summary&timestamp=451.0)\n  - [Plans to communicate \"more early and often\" in team channels](https://fathom.video/share/uzLphizGENVWAcHcGLNW9mzb_HYPrCKo?tab=summary&timestamp=451.0)\n  - [Recognizes importance of kickoff context for entire team](https://fathom.video/share/uzLphizGENVWAcHcGLNW9mzb_HYPrCKo?tab=summary&timestamp=451.0)\n\n### Unexpected Schedule Gap\n\n  - [Discovered 10-minute gap in meeting schedule](https://fathom.video/share/uzLphizGENVWAcHcGLNW9mzb_HYPrCKo?tab=summary&timestamp=441.0)\n  - [Brief discussion on rarity of free time on Monday afternoons](https://fathom.video/share/uzLphizGENVWAcHcGLNW9mzb_HYPrCKo?tab=summary&timestamp=257.0)\n\n## Next Steps\n\n  - [Implement 5-minute post-kickoff debrief process](https://fathom.video/share/uzLphizGENVWAcHcGLNW9mzb_HYPrCKo?tab=summary&timestamp=30.0)\n  - [George to improve frequency & timeliness of sharing kickoff insights](https://fathom.video/share/uzLphizGENVWAcHcGLNW9mzb_HYPrCKo?tab=summary&timestamp=451.0)\n  - [Schedule call to debrief on Bubble kickoff](https://fathom.video/share/uzLphizGENVWAcHcGLNW9mzb_HYPrCKo?tab=summary&timestamp=474.0)\n  - [Review George's compiled feedback from recent kickoff calls](https://fathom.video/share/uzLphizGENVWAcHcGLNW9mzb_HYPrCKo?tab=summary&timestamp=481.0)\n  - [Consider grouping similar companies for future kickoff scheduling](https://fathom.video/share/uzLphizGENVWAcHcGLNW9mzb_HYPrCKo?tab=summary&timestamp=81.0)\n"
